title: Hard Starboard Radio: Paul Ryan, Jack Ryan, What's The Difference? | Opinion - Conservative
text:
(Before It's News)
Why are we dragging Paul Ryan, kicking and screaming, into the Speaker’s chair?; Crisis of a House divided that Tea Partiers will not allow to stand; SHOULD Paul Ryan run?; The GOP needs a House Speaker whom all party factions can trust; How the Freedom Caucus “strategy” will backfire on them; and the Political Pistachio headlines of the day.
Back in time for the weekend on Open Thighs Friday at 6PM Eastern/3PM Pacific .
